This file is to be a working document covering what the Simple Game Engine (Simple GE) website will consist of.

1. What is it? 
This website will be a pure documentation website going over the Simple Game Engine framework. 
This framework has been created and updated by The Open Source Artist and is currently being used for our game projects like Frogger and Snake and will be used for the upcoming game "Bubs Last Resort".

2. What aspects/features will be included? 
The website itself will consist of several sections within the side navigation bar. The sections within the navigation will cover each aspect of the framework, such as explaining "Entities" and how to properly use them when developing. 

3. Who is it for? 
For anyone who's interested! Interested in learning how to build games with a custome Pygame framework developed to make building classic games as simple as possible. 


